    "The large volumes of data generated through screening, assessment, and treatment will require secure, encrypted storage to protect patient privacy and guard against cybersecurity threats.",
    "Anonymized datasets may become valuable resources for research, with interest from SLPs, data mining companies, and insurance companies.",
    "University clinics with access to such data may establish data-sharing platforms to support global collaboration among SLPs.",
